                            <emph>Israel</emph>. | H: <emph>in</emph>
                            <emph>Israel</emph>. | C: <emph>in</emph>
                            <emph>Israel</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote">An interpretative addition to Num
                            23:23.</note>
                        <note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote">An interpretative addition to Num
                            23:23.</note>
                        <note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote">A mistranslation based on interpreting
                            Heb. <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">הַיְשִׁימֹן </foreign>
                            ‘the wasteland’ as a place name.</note>
